# ğŸ¥ Healthcare Backend API

A RESTful Healthcare Management Backend built using **Django**, **Django REST Framework**, **PostgreSQL**, and **JWT Authentication**.

This system enables secure user authentication and management of patients, doctors, and their relationships through protected API endpoints.

